data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Discover the charm of this delightful rambler nestled in a picturesque neighborhood. Located on the east bench of Ogden, this home boasts a breathtaking mountain view. This hidden gem is eagerly awaiting your personal touch to restore it to its full potential. With a spacious back yard, this property offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gardening, or even creating your own private oasis. Situated on a generous corner lot, this home offers both privacy and convenience. The best part? This incredible property comes at a great price, making it an exceptional opportunity for those seeking a blend of character, potential and affordability. Don't miss out on the chance to transform this house into your dream home! Square footage figures are provided as an estimate only. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
